                              Refrain version 1.0.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  refrain <mode> <name> <--options>

                                Available options
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Options                                           Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  --help -h                                         Display help and then exit.

                                 Available Input
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Input                                             Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  mode                                               Either create or compile.
  name                                               The name of the sub-directory to create/compile. If left out when creating, the default will be "newProject". If left out when compiling, the current directory will be compiled.

                                      Modes
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Input                                             Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  create                                             Create a new project directory in the current directory. This doesn't work properly if there is already a directory in the current directory with the same name as the project.
  compile                                            Compile the current directory assuming it is a proper Refrain project.